			<div class="content" id="post-content-3648564">
									

<p>This isn't a filler tale, nor is it a stopgap in the story.</p>
<p>I mean yeah this is depressing, but I'm relatively fine now. It's okay. Sorry for the one-day delay in posting; new Hearthstone expansion, and all that.</p>
<p>Don't remove the researcher-talloran tag. It's relevant.</p>
<p>Image is my own, licensed under CC 3.0.</p>
<hr />
<p>Updates Mondays and Thursdays.</p>

