			<div class="content" id="post-content-3650572">
									

<p>Peeling back the layers is doing this story favours. If you described this to me in the abstract, I'm not sure I would be enthusiastic, but it's working on the page. I agree that this didn't come across as depressing, in the same way there's a difference between a story about terror and a terrifying story.</p>
<p>For the record though, I am shocked (shocked!) that you saw fit to share my private sentiments in a public story. How can I continue to assert that <span style="text-decoration: underline;">every author ever</span> should specifically tailor their work to best suit my specific tastes and needs? I'll look like some kind of hypocrite! ;)</p>

							</div>

								
					
