														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3650746">
									

<p>Perhaps I haven't been paying attention. Picking up on metaphors and symbolism has never been something I'm good at. I just don't think breaking the fourth wall this much is a good way to tell a story. I understand that is what you set out to do. Congratulations on making it this far, you've done better than I ever could. But I don't like it.</p>

